  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales Consultant",
  "description": "<h3><u><strong>About Us</strong></u></h3><p>We are a licensed employment agency in Singapore, working closely with <strong>local employers</strong> to solve their hiring needs. If you enjoy meeting people, closing deals and growing a client base, we want you on our team.<br /></p><h3><u><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></u></h3><ul><li>Hunt for new clients & follow-up existing clients</li><li>Sell recruitment and manpower solutions.</li><li>Understand hiring needs and match the right talent.</li><li>Manage clients from first call to deal closure.</li><li>Build long-term clients relationships.</li><li>Hit sales targets and get rewarded.</li></ul><h3><u><strong>What We're Looking For</strong></u></h3><ul><li>CEI Basic Certificate (mandatory)</li><li>Prior experience in recruitment or sales will be an advantage.</li><li>Confident communicate who enjoys talking to clients.</li><li>Self-driven, energetic and target-oriented.</li><li>Comfortable working independently.</li></ul><h3><u><strong>Salary & Perks</strong></u></h3><ul><li>Basic Salary: SGD $2500-$3500</li><li>Training provided & Team player</li><li>Career growth opportunities </li><li>Attractive commission for every single closure</li></ul><h3><u><strong>Location & Hours</strong></u></h3><p>Bukit Timah, Singapore | 5 days work week (Flexible)<br /></p>",
