    "description": "<p><strong>Nayaka Services</strong> is a licensed employment agency and ticketing agent in Singapore. Nayaka Services is a member of the <strong>Tripartite Alliance for Fair and Progressive Employment Practices (TAFEP)</strong> in Singapore. It is one of the approved agency by <strong>Ministry of Manpower to deploy Household Service Scheme (HSS)</strong> workers for domestic cleaning services.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>It has strong manpower partner relationships in countries such as China, Bangladesh, Indonesia, India, Myanmar, Taiwan, Sri Lanka, Philippines.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Nayaka Services</strong> is <em><strong>accredited</strong></em> with <strong>Sri Lanka High Commission</strong> and <strong>Embassy of the Philippines </strong>which aids in our recruitment and deployment of foreign manpower in Singapore.</p>",
